description.plain:
Kimberose is a pop-soul French band formed in 2015 by bandleaders Kimberly, Anthony Hadjadj and Alexandre Delange.

Their first EP It’s Probably Me was released in september 29 2017. The band played their song “I’m Sorry” on a French live TV emission.

Their debut album, Chapter One was released on March 16 2018.

Current lineup consists of Kimberly Kitson Mills (lead vocals), Alexandre Delange (piano and vocals), Anthony Hadjadj (guitar and vocals), François Fuchs (bassist) and Fred Drouillard (drums).
